snippet.title: Advance Wars 1+2: Re-Boot Camp - Nintendo Treehouse: Live | E3 2021
snippet.description:
Lace up your boots and move out with the gameplay debut of #AdvanceWars 1+2: Re-Boot Camp! Advance Wars 1+2: Re-Boot Camp launches 12/3. 

Learn more here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/advance-wars-1-plus-2-re-boot-camp-switch/
